Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was discharged?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  Mr. Johan Liebert left this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.68,0:00:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he had suddenly collapsed, but\NI guess it wasn't all that serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that girl who always comes to the library...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the librarian at the college library...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, he was discharged?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what had happened to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He collapsed right in front of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was looking for a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was helping him look for it, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he suddenly collapsed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and he was screaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was holding a picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, when he flipped the page like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:24.91,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(355,0)\pos(354,340)}At the End of the Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be resting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they didn't find anything wrong with your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're perfectly healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor said that it might have \N been caused by anemia or fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you had an emotional shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the doctor said, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never knew about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a big scar on your head from an operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, you should forget about\Nworking, and just study for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter for you arrived while you were in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no return address on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think it is a letter bomb, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from the "Red Hindenburg."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a pretty one has wandered in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you trying it for the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gently teach you everything, starting at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where the Red Hindenburg is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:04:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written here that the Red Hindenburg\Nis somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At your age?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've sure got some weird tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's down that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pills...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some pills...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Red Hindenburg up ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. That's the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a pretty face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 saw you on the news with Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After calling yourself Margot Langer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you now call yourself the Red Hindenburg?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until recently, I was Blue Sophie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Names don't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Johan Liebert?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:06:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's what my boyfriend calls me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My boyfriend who's on the other side of that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wouldn't think about doing anything foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a really big gun cocked \N on the other side of that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a really big cock too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a meticulous plan to get back\Nat that rich bastard Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm really impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought in a kid named Fahren once, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never thought Schuwald's real \N son would appear after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for Fahren.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once there was no more use for \N him, he committed suicide. .
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it took two years to get here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, the real Margot Langer passed away\Nat the perfect time two years ago too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And her passing sure helped me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I was really close to her anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't a street walker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had cleaned herself up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just had a drink two or three times, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably didn't have anyone to talk to for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got her a little drunk, showed some crocodile\Ntears, and she told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her love affair with Schuwald...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The son she gave up for adoption...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then that woman got herself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, I played the role of Margot Langer \N and got a big pile of cash from Schuwald!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:08:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the police filed Margot's case\Nas just another phantom killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think the police would've ever suspected\Nthat a plan like this was in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That detective Richard was a sad case, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only he hadn't interfered.. .
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he wouldn't have had to "commit suicide."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, how many people have you killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's cut the small talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much are you willing to offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think the most frightening thing is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had seen the darkest place...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing the subject isn't going to do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But beyond that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have found an even deeper darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can just leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in Schuwald anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you look down on me, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Honey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roberto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have a balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can buy your pills with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:10.21,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fad(283,0)\pos(344,334)}Carstensen Street \N (Munich)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done yet, Doctor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His head is bleeding
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts! It hurts! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My child comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts! It hurts! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut him up! It's just a broken bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, he is  so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you two stop arguing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and just sit down and wait your turn
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much commotion you guys make, \N there's only one good doctor around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that long stick thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... it's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the doctor here really good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this doctor wasn't here, all the Asians around here \N would be dead by now, especially the Vietnamese.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not Vietnamese, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:11:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look too good, but the injured come first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not really a patient or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, just sit down and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and take a look at him, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My son first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in line, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I'd like to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go wait outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 don't have time for you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's very...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how old is this doctor...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the middle of suturing, so don't bother me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to this patient, it'll be your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A stab wound to the femur...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caused by a knife...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her suture is pretty clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should insert a drainage tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't, you should take him to a real hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A real hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell just by looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a real doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could take him to a real hospital,\NI would've done so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The majority of the people here are either\Nillegal residents or illegal immigrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they went to a real hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'd be sent to an institution immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then deported back to their home country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how many people around here died\Nbecause they couldn't go to a real hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk big when you don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insert a drainage tube!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a good chance that he was\Nstabbed with a dirty knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't treat him with a drain insertion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the wound will fester...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and an abscess will form!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Undo one or two stitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insert the drainage tube about 5cm deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everything went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it from a patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been taking care of them for 48\Nhours straight without sleep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also looked at the conditions of\Nthe patients after their surgeries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was pretty good for an unlicensed doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventeen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised at how skilled you are at your age...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're like a real medical practitioner...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor that opened his practice here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just happened to disappear without any explanation,\Nand left his equipment behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't something you can do just\Nbecause you have the equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you learn skills like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because my father... was a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was a Vietnamese doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took me with him to East Germany to study abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then he stayed, and opened up a small clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then the Wall came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with his limited ability, he tried to save the Asians...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so they targeted him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was killed by some punks\Ncalling themselves the neo-Nazis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was killed because his skin color was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 was suddenly alone, and was sent off to an orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, 1 was taken in by a German family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they only took me in, out of\Na sense of social obligation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just a poor little yellow-skinned girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.73,0:16:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had been helping my father ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also read many of,the medical\Nbooks my father left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I decided to follow in his footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it to heal quickly, then take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, will the next patient...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go home and study properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country gives chances to those who want to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you're a real doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to say that amateurs\Nshould just step aside, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go away, what's going to happen to these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's going to take care of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My p-pimp went nuts... and pulled a gun... on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She walked all the way here after she was shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy said you can treat her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help my mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:17:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They always end up like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do something to help her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is impossible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get her onto the operating table!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lift that side up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go to a real hospital for something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be too late if we carry her to a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know my limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can t do anything about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the patient is still breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't give up hope until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't throw away your hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If her intraabdominal arteries were damaged...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her blood pressure would immediately drop...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she'd go into a state of shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if she managed to walk all the way here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:19:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her blood pressure is steadily dropping,\Nand she's in a state of pre-shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by this gunshot wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a good chance that part\Nof the spleen was damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means there's still hope if we perform an\Nemergency laparotomy while making a blood transfusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's begin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up the scalpel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's sound asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, her bones, intestines, and digestive\Nsystem weren't damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were fortunate that we only had \N to remove the damaged spleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an excellent operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all because you were there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here because there was something \N I wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This news article...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Sophie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also known as the Red Hindenburg...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you were the first to arrive at\Nthe murder scene of this prostitute...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you tell me what the crime scene looked like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That night, I came rushing in after receiving\Na call from someone in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had been shot in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death was instantaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen numerous crime scenes like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this was the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling when 1 entered that room...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a robbery...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was... simply killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay in the darkness, \N you'll sink into the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine light upon it..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me. Study hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can become a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll be a good doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like you're falling into\Na deeper darkness than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll come back again, won't you, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:31.01,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(175,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:44.44,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(188,474)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:44.44,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(193,23)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:47.40,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:23:01.08,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(188,474)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:23:01.08,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(191,20)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:25.94,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(190,474)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:34.36,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(189,471)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:36.82,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,471)}Make it home
